      <title>桑迪胡克幸存者将在没有 20 名同学的情况下怀着复杂的心情毕业</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/12/nx-s1-5002981/sandy-hook-shooting-survivors-graduate-newtown-high-school</link>
